= reflection > capture â€” daily logs

intent
  capture "thoughts" (interactive)
  stamp "time" (utc)
  store "journal" (sys_journal)

logic
  input: interactive (stdin)
  delimiter: `---`
  
  process
    read lines until delimiter
    if empty, abort
    store to memory (type=sys_journal)
    
  output
    confirmation "journaled."

commands
  py journal                | interactive entry for current agent
  py journal <agent>        | interactive entry for specific agent

integration
  SovereignAgent (memory)
